This paper is about natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on extractive summarization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
